OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FThe long-awaited Hillsborough Law will
OL,7,Fcontain a legal duty of candour "with
OL,8,Fcriminal sanctions for those who do
OL,9,Fnot comply", the government has said.
OL,11,FThe confirmation comes after Labour MP
OL,12,FAnneliese Midgley, raised a question
OL,13,Fin the House of Commons around whether
OL,14,Fan obligation for public servants to
OL,15,Ftell the truth in the wake of a major
OL,16,Fincident or disaster would be included
OL,17,Fin the Bill, after concerns it would
OL,18,Fbe watered down.
