OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FThe MP for Knowsley, in Merseyside,
OL,7,Falso asked when ministers would
OL,8,Fintroduce the legislation, months
OL,9,Fafter the Government had originally
OL,10,Fsaid it would be presented.
OL,12,FThe Government confirmed the Bill will
OL,13,Fcontain a legal "duty of candour" -
OL,14,Fstating public servants could face
OL,15,Fjail if they are found not to have
OL,16,Ftold the truth during investigations
OL,17,For inquiries.
