OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FMs Midgley said: "The families have
OL,7,Fbeen campaigning for a Hillsborough
OL,8,FLaw for 36 years, and their demand has
OL,9,Falways been clear. A law with the duty
OL,10,Fof candour at its heart.
OL,12,F"Too many broken promises and missed
OL,13,Fdeadlines. So can the solicitor
OL,14,Fgeneral tell me when will the
OL,15,FGovernment bring forward the
OL,16,FHillsborough Law, and will it honour
OL,17,Fthe promises made to victims of state
OL,18,Fcover-ups and finally deliver justice
OL,19,Ffor the 97."
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOU{D@LO]
