OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FThe proposed law is named after the
OL,7,Ffootball stadium in Sheffield, where a
OL,8,Fcrush during a 1989 FA Cup semi-final
OL,9,Fbetween Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,10,FForest led to the death of 97 football
OL,11,Ffans.
OL,13,FThe Government previously introduced a
OL,14,FBill which was criticised by
OL,15,Fcampaigners and legal experts for not
OL,16,Fhaving a legally binding duty of
OL,17,Fcandour.
OL,19,FIt was pulled over concerns related to
OL,20,Fwho the duty of candour would apply to.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
