OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FCampaigners fear another Bill could be
OL,7,Freintroduced that would still be
OL,8,Finsufficient as it would not be shared
OL,9,Fwith families beforehand.
OL,11,FLabour previously said the law would
OL,12,Fbe introduced before the 36th
OL,13,Fanniversary in April 2025.
OL,15,FSolicitor General Lucy Rigby said Ms
OL,16,FMidgley had been a "resolute and
OL,17,Fsteadfast" campaigner for Hillsborough
OL,18,Ffamilies.
OL,26,@xD@TOUyD@JO]
