OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FMs Rigby told MPs: "The Government,
OL,7,Fincluding the Prime Minister, have
OL,8,Fbeen working closely with the
OL,9,Ffamilies, and I can confirm that the
OL,10,Fdraft Bill will include a statutory
OL,11,Fduty of candour for public servants,
OL,12,Fwith criminal sanctions for those who
OL,13,Fdo not comply.
OL,15,F"Measures to decisively tackle the
OL,16,Fdisparity between the state and
OL,17,Fbereaved families at inquests too.
OL,26,@nD@TOUwD@AOU
