OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,F"As to timing, I know everyone is
OL,7,Fworking extremely hard to get this
OL,8,Flegislation right, and the Government
OL,9,Fhopes to be in a position to introduce
OL,10,Fa Bill to Parliament very soon."
OL,12,FIt came a day after a Westminster Hall
OL,13,Fdebate was told by a former Labour
OL,14,Fshadow chancellor that the party could
OL,15,Fface a frosty reception in Liverpool
OL,16,Fwhen its four-day conference begins on
OL,17,F28 September.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@`O]
