OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FIndependent MP John McDonnell (Hayes
OL,7,Fand Harlington) said: "I want to make
OL,8,Fthis point very, very clear. Labour is
OL,9,Fgoing for its conference in three
OL,10,Fweeks time to Liverpool.
OL,12,F"If this legislation is not sorted by
OL,13,Fthen, do not expect a welcome in
OL,14,FLiverpool from the people there,
OL,15,Fbecause we've waited too long."
OL,17,FLabour MP Ian Byrne (Liverpool West
OL,18,FDerby) was at Hillsborough more than
OL,19,F35 years ago, and his father was
OL,20,Finjured in the disaster.
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@AOUwD@_O]
