OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FHe added: "The time for delaying is
OL,7,Fover. The time for diluted promises is
OL,8,Fover. We must legislate, we must
OL,9,Fprotect truth, and we must honour
OL,10,Fthose who have died at the hands of
OL,11,Fthe state, and those who have fought
OL,12,Ffor justice on their behalf. Not with
OL,13,Fwords, but with law."
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@UO]
