OL,3,CLong-awaited Hillsborough Law 'will
OL,4,Ccontain a legal duty of candour'
OL,6,FJustice minister Alex Davies-Jones had
OL,7,Ftold the debate: "It has taken some
OL,8,Ftime to get this right. But we are
OL,9,Fcommitted to introducing the
OL,10,FHillsborough law, with parity of arms,
OL,11,Fand that statutory legal duty of
OL,12,Fcandour, and we hope to bring that
OL,13,Fforward as soon as possible.
OL,15,F"We have worked in conjunction with
OL,16,Ffamilies and campaigners to make sure
OL,17,Fthat we've got that right, and we feel
OL,18,Fwe are almost there."
OL,26,@oD@ROUwD@AOUzD@UO]
